@Rankoon_HostAddress = http://localhost:5020

### Get Weather Forecast
GET {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Discord Login URL
GET {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Discord Login URL with Return URL
GET {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login?returnUrl=/dashboard
Accept: application/json

###

### Refresh Token (replace with actual refresh token)
POST {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your_refresh_token_here"
}

###

### Logout (replace with actual refresh token)
POST {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your_refresh_token_here"
}

###

### Get Current User (requires Authorization header with JWT token)
GET {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User Guilds (requires Authorization header with JWT token)
GET {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/api/auth/guilds
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Authentication (requires Authorization header with JWT token)
GET {{Rankoon_HostAddress}}/api/auth/test
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Accept: application/json

###
